<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lazy-adj">lazy <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'leɪzi/    美 /'leɪzi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>懒惰的；懒散的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was not stupid, just lazy.
他不傻，只是懒。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>lazily /'leɪzɪlɪ/ adv <br />
laziness /'leɪzinəs/ n [U]   </p></div>